{"tid":1379512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到宜家仲政治冷感既人我屌曬你地老母","createTime":"2019-07-28T20:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:59:11.000Z","uid":291221,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"118c2d7c25024df3e703bb75ee3e35ba1ff3503b","tid":1379512,"uid":291221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"經歷左咁多次遊行<br />\n作為和理非 都發過唔少次夢<br />\n但係聽到啲港豬係咁屌前線收錢 暴力<br />\n自己連發生咩事都唔知<br />\n真係好撚心痛<br />\n前線手足為左我地犧牲<br />\n點解仲要係咁亂屌？<br />\n如果無前線 我地和理非 甚至班港豬算係咩<br />\n我地係直頭唔配有前線為我地做咁多嘢<br />\n前線手足唔好失望 唔好心淡 <br />\n就算人地唔明白 至少我 同一班兄弟撐你地<br />\n絕不割蓆  <br />\n香港人 加油。<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"bfba555e50a07c19ef3047ba3fb41c0d4a489c73","tid":1379512,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:21:29.000Z","msg":"返工嗰度全深藍咁滯<br />\n有時真係好難唔心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28625bdc260cad72cdfe1deabebc2fc415289693","tid":1379512,"uid":291221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfba555e50a07c19ef3047ba3fb41c0d4a489c73","tid":1379512,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T20:21:29.000Z","msg":"返工嗰度全深藍咁滯<br />\n有時真係好難唔心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"啲廢物真係多一個都嫌多"},{"pid":"eeb6b0cf59bcc5e6778d2d959ea7c67a915a16ef","tid":1379512,"uid":55198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"條街有好多學生俾警犬打到頭破血流<br />\n<br />\n仲有人有心情開/睇演唱會<br />\n<br />\n我真係理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbed8431bb724025a7fffe98b95a01784346efb","tid":1379512,"uid":291221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeb6b0cf59bcc5e6778d2d959ea7c67a915a16ef","tid":1379512,"uid":55198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"條